detailed_description:
A hammer disguised as a body pillow. Though their appearances differ, it has the same properties as a vibrohammer. Because Fencer weapons tended to look intimidating, complaints were voiced by townspeople near the base. In response to these complaints, development decided to make a disguise that wasn't intimidating at all. Furthermore, it has a peaceful paint job to give it a more agreeable appearance.<br />
<br />
The hammer causes an immense vibration on impact, shattering not just the object struck, but those around it. &quot;

